        {
            "id": 6312913,
            "title": "台股30檔千金股同框聚首 華城、雙鴻、勤誠取得準千金門票",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今 (16) 日衝上 31300 點之上，再度改寫歷史新高，而台股今天 30 檔千金股齊聚，並有 6 檔準千金備戰中，其中，包括華城 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1519:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1519\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1519-TW</a>)、雙鴻 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3324:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3324\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3324-TW</a>) 以及勤誠 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8210:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8210\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8210-TW</a>) 皆有望晉身千金股行列。 </p></section><p><template id=\"P:1\"></template></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 昨 (15) 日法說會報喜，今日股價走揚，盤中最高衝上 1740 元，創歷史新天價，也同步帶動大盤突破 31300 點。繼昨日收盤首見 30 檔千金股齊聚後，今天再度合體，而千金股前十名為信驊 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5274:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5274\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5274-TW</a>)、緯穎(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6669:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6669\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6669-TW</a>)、鴻勁(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7769:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7769\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7769-TW</a>)、穎崴(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6515:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6515\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6515-TW</a>)、川湖(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2059:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2059\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2059-TW</a>)、世芯 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3661:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3661\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3661-TW</a>)、創意(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3443:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3443\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3443-TW</a>)、大立光(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3008:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3008\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3008-TW</a>)、健策(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3653:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3653\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3653-TW</a>) 及精測(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6510:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6510\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6510-TW</a>)。 </p></section><section>\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>另外，有 6 檔股價在 900 元之上，包含致茂 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2360:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2360\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2360-TW</a>)、雙鴻、華城、勤誠、昇達科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3491:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3491\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3491-TW</a>) 及新應材 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:4749:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4749\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4749-TW</a>)，取得準千金股資格。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>華城於 2024 年 7 月股價衝上 1030 元，創下歷史新天價，而今天盤中最高衝上 992 元，漲逾半根停板，千金股近在咫尺。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>另外，今天台美對等關稅稅率從現行 20%，調降至 15%，華城銷美比重較高，去年前 11 月外銷占比就超過 55%，因此關稅稅率調降，對華城而言是一大利多。除關稅負擔降低，華城也持續受惠因 AI 發展所帶動的電網與電力基礎建設需求，去年全年營收達 244.23 億元，年增 20.89%，創歷史新高。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>雙鴻與勤誠也都於 2025 年 11 月站上千金，歷史新高價皆為 1110 元。不過兩者今天相對無表現，皆於平盤附近遊走。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6312913",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-16 12:13:38",
            "source": "cnyes",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "id": 6312926,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 詮欣(6205)大跌7.07%，報57.8元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>詮欣(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6205:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6205\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6205-TW</a>)16日12:14股價下跌4.4元，報57.8元，跌幅7.07%，成交2,451張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>詮欣(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6205:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6205\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6205-TW</a>)所屬產業為電子零組件業，主要業務為各種電子零件(連接器、電子線)等製造加工買賣業務。一般進出口貿易業務(期貨除外)。有關前項業務之代理經銷報價及投標業務。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲3.49%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲1.48%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-301 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-173 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-128 張</li> <li>融資增減：-199 張</li> <li>融券增減：-4 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
